                        <interp inst="t18370227-name-1130" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM DICKENSON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant H</hi> 11) I took the prisoners, and got the timber from Siples' yard.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Griffith's Defence.</hi> This man met me, and asked me if I wanted a job—he took me to assist in getting this timber—he asked if I knew of a place to put it in, and I took it to Mrs. Siples', as I knew her.</p>
